3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the recognition of human emotions, which is a subfield of AI. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with emotion recognition in images and videos. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper deals with recognizing human emotions, which is relevant to HCI research.
